he had reason to believe

00:38:55.190 --> 00:38:59.470
that if the map turned
up after his death,

00:38:59.470 --> 00:39:02.860
it would confront German
Nazi culture bearers

00:39:02.860 --> 00:39:04.850
with a difficult choice.

00:39:04.850 --> 00:39:09.860
