01:06:32.170 --> 01:06:35.770 position:56%
about my conclusions, and maybe
during the question session it would

01:06:35.770 --> 01:06:40.320
be nice to sort of look at
what is the analogy or not.

01:06:40.320 --> 01:06:44.070 position:56%
Again, the Vinland map is
essentially written in one language,

01:06:44.070 --> 01:06:48.230
has a fairly clear agenda,
one that was just elucidated

01:06:48.230 --> 01:06:53.780 position:56%
in the proceeding talk, and even the
cartography itself very explicitly

01:06:53.780 --> 01:06:58.030
says look here up in
this portion of the map.

01:06:58.030 --> 01:07:02.950
The Rossi maps obviously make lots
of allusions to the far northeast,

01:07:02.950 --> 01:07:06.570
but there's never find of the
explicit claim, for example,

01:07:06.570 --> 01:07:09.070
that Marco Polo reached America.

01:07:09.070 --> 01:07:10.370
