01:38:02.410 --> 01:38:06.490
but I was really intrigued to note
how the town really embraces it

01:38:06.490 --> 01:38:11.080
as a legitimate valid
map of their town.

01:38:11.080 --> 01:38:14.790
And so I had done a little looking
around at some of the details

01:38:14.790 --> 01:38:17.200
on their map, and I have been able

01:38:17.200 --> 01:38:22.140
to identify four different place
