01:38:30.130 --> 01:38:31.660
and you identify everything for me,

01:38:31.660 --> 01:38:33.010
and they would work
that into the map.

01:38:33.010 --> 01:38:37.820
So in that sense you can see
how the town would embrace it.

01:38:37.820 --> 01:38:40.300
Yeah, this represents our town.

01:38:40.300 --> 01:38:45.270
And here are four more examples
