02:02:50.800 --> 02:02:52.100
&gt;&gt; Yes.

02:02:52.100 --> 02:02:54.060
&gt;&gt; Kirsten Seaver: Now that's
a very interesting history

02:02:54.060 --> 02:03:01.710
because there was a book dealer,
an antiquarian book dealer

02:03:01.710 --> 02:03:09.000
from Massachusetts, who went
to Switzerland and linked

02:03:09.000 --> 02:03:14.390
up with Italian book
dealer who had long operated

02:03:14.390 --> 02:03:19.340
in Switzerland as well as in Spain.

02:03:19.340 --> 02:03:23.420
His wife was Spanish.

02:03:23.420 --> 02:03:29.630 position:56%
And picking over what was said at
the time about the purchase and what

02:03:29.630 --> 02:03:40.810 position:56%
in fact happened over time, this was
a collusion to make money, you know,

02:03:40.810 --> 02:03:44.750
sort of gradually, by
passing the manuscript

02:03:44.750 --> 02:03:49.310
on through various channels and
making it look like a coincidence

02:03:49.310 --> 02:03:53.840
that the Vinland map, the tarter
relation, and somehow the holes

02:03:53.840 --> 02:04:00.290 position:56%
in the Speculum Historiale in the
old dilapidated binding all matched.

02:04:00.290 --> 02:04:03.820
Well actually I've looked at the
thing, and there's only one hole

02:04:03.820 --> 02:04:06.510
that matches, and that
is one that looks

02:04:06.510 --> 02:04:10.370
like it's going straight
through like that.

02:04:10.370 --> 02:04:12.480
This is all very peculiar.

02:04:12.480 --> 02:04:17.640
The way in which the two
so-called sister texts ended

02:04:17.640 --> 02:04:22.960
up at Yale is also very
strange because it has to do

02:04:22.960 --> 02:04:29.490
with antiquarian book deals that
sort of went back and forth with,

02:04:29.490 --> 02:04:33.020
you know, one person sells
it, the other one buys it

02:04:33.020 --> 02:04:37.450
and then sells it back
to the next person again,

02:04:37.450 --> 02:04:41.860
and it was all done
to make it look legit.

02:04:41.860 --> 02:04:48.620
This is just a snake operation from
start to finish by the time it got

02:04:48.620 --> 02:04:51.770
out of Father Fischer's hands.

02:04:51.770 --> 02:04:55.960
My guess is that after he died

02:04:55.960 --> 02:05:02.130
